#eNCA speaks to Psychologist and Founder of Motsha Teens, Pretty Kekana. #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - Mental health is not a new discussion in South Africa, and many young people in our country suffer silently without knowing where to get help. Motsha Teens is an NGO that helps young people deal with mental health at a grassroots level. The organisation currently helps more than a hundred youngsters. eNCA speaks to Psychologist and Founder of Motsha Teens, Pretty Kekana in the video above.